        <h1 class="absolute top-1/6 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 text-base-300 text-bold text-3xl sm:text-7xl yeseva-one-regular">DIT LIVS EVENTYR!</h1>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>

